"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        (gimp-context-set-background '(255 255 255) )\n"
"        (gimp-context-set-foreground inTextColor)\n"
"      "

#: src/using/script-fu-tutorial.xml:1139(para)
msgid ""
"With the colors properly set, let's now clean out the garbage currently in "
